o show you, I'll bring a photograph to show you him taken with his cycle which was a penny farthing, and - you'll be most interested. Well my father was a big cyclist and therefore he bought us all a cycle, we all - all the children had a bicycle and we u
sed - and when we were young we used to go cycling with him. And when I was - thirteen, I left school, I went with my father to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}London{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
