 and - the year we went - the year we went to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}London{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 was the year that Selfridges store was being built. 'Cos I remember walking past the front of it while it was being built, walking over the ramps. And there was no motor cars in those days, they were just horse buses and - and cyclists.
