s and that sort of thing. And he always had a - he had a nasty cough. I know when I - when I - when I got married I went to live on the opposite side of the street and I could tell when my father was going up the street, if I didn't see him, I could tell 
by his cough, as he was walking up - as he was walking passed. Yes, always had a bad cough.
