 he deserted the ship. And of course they couldn't find him so the ship had to come away without him. But he said he actually saw - he was in hiding and he saw the sh
ip come away without him. Well - we didn't hear anything from him for a long long time and he was roaming about Australia, he was at Melbourne and - he did - he got all sorts of jobs, working in stables and sort of living at the bush and all that sort of 
