ason he was sent away - my father thought he would be a bad influence on me and my younger brother. However, after he'd been home again we'll say for six months or so he wanted to go back again to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname country-region}}Australia{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. So me father said, right. You go. She paid his passage out to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname country-region}}Australia
