st - the first world war. And - my father - the 1914-'8 - and before - before the war started my brother got - he began to associate with a young lady and my father thought, well perhaps it'd do him good if he got married you see, thought perhaps it'd set
tle him down. However me father give him every encouragement to get married and he bought a little business for him in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Stafford{\*\xmlclose}
