\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7343200 OB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6423686\charrsid7763791 I'd known her for four years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2775584 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6423686\charrsid7763791 How did you meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7343200 OB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6423686\charrsid7763791 
How did I meet? Now then, this a most interesting little story. Most interesting. And it must be very interesting to know how certain people met their wives. Well, I'll tell you, we - we - we boys who had known each other at school and 
were all - were working, we used to gather just outside the gates at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}Logton{\*\xmlclose} {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceType}}Park{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
. And there was like a gas lamp outside and a - and a - a path round it where we could stand round this gas lamp talking, and the traffic could pass all the way round it if it 
had be. So there came a young - there came a young lady passed. And - she walked - she - she was on the other side of the road walking towards Blurton and of course you know how - you know how - lads just look at these girls and pass comments - pass }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1074794\charrsid7763791 comments}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6423686\charrsid7763791 
 you see, and - one of them said, I'll bet you daren't go and speak to her? So she went - she went by and then she came back again, and as she came back on the opposite side of the road walking home, I left these lads and - I went as I - I - as I was wal
king home too when I got to the side of her I said, good evening. And then she - and when she turned to - towards me I realized that she wasn't the girl that we'd been talking about. This girl - this - this girl was a Miss Jones you see, that went by and 
t
hey were strangers, they were a new family that had come into the district. However, when I said good evening to her she turned towards me and just smiled and - and I walked - I walked on with her which was - which was only a short distance farther on. Ju
st in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Belgrave Road{\*\xmlclose}, {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Dresden{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
. You know where that is do you? Yes, yes. And then - I used to meet her quite often - without making any appointment with her, it seemed rather peculiar. But I used to meet her. Out. And - I courted her quite a long time and yet
 I never used to - never used to make an arrangement that I would see her again, but somehow I always - I did - I did do. And - as I told you - I'd been very fond of the girls and I knew a lot of girls but she was just different than all the others that I
'd ever talked to.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2775584 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6423686\charrsid7763791 So this made her special?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7343200 OB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6423686\charrsid7763791 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2775584 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6423686\charrsid7763791 Where did she come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7343200 OB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6423686\charrsid7763791 They came from Tork. Torkus Hill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2775584 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6423686\charrsid7763791 Did you save up money before getting married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7343200 OB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6423686\charrsid7763791 Yes. I saved - I saved enough to get married out of ten shillings a week.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2775584 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6423686\charrsid7763791 Did your parents help you in setting up home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7343200 OB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6423686\charrsid7763791 
They did help me as regards - all sorts of utensils, because we were in that type of business but the furniture I bought myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2775584 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6423686\charrsid7763791 How long were you engaged?
