\ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6423686\charrsid7763791  in those days, there was no windscreen, there was no hood - so - if you wanted a windscreen that was an extra and if you wanted a hood that was extra and a motor car, a fo
ur seater motor car in those days cost about a hundred and eighty-five pounds and beautiful coachwork. The coachwork was lovely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2775584 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6423686\charrsid7763791 
Can you remember what you felt like sitting in this automobile or driving round }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1074794\charrsid7763791 L}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6423686\charrsid7763791 ongton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7343200 OB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6423686\charrsid7763791 Oh yes, yes. And we used to
 - we used to have a little ride in this - on a car on a Sunday, and if went from - if we went from Longton to Dandon we'd had a terrific ride. If you'd done - if you'd done about twenty mile it had been marvellous.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2775584 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6423686\charrsid7763791 Did people stop to stare at it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7343200 OB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6423686\charrsid7763791 
Well everybody, yes, everybody started at the early motor cars. Yes. And you had - you had a big horn, a clonk, clonk, clonk, you know, a good big noisy horn.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2775584 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6423686\charrsid7763791 Did you feel somewhat good and important having this motor car?
