es, yes. Yes. And my brother - my brother was a mechanic, me father sent him to the - he sent him to the works where this car came from in Wolverhampton for a short period to get an insight of the motor car.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2775584 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6423686\charrsid7763791 What was the motor car, can you remember?
