ly very good at school, in fact he was so good at school that - they went for him to go to Hanley to the Education Offices, they wanted to see him, to have a talk to him. And when the war - when the war came on, the second war came on he - he joined in th
e - he joined the Air Force and he became a - a pilot. And the other boy - the other - the elder - his elder brother was in the Army. Sell -
