im - we put him to - we articled - he was articled to - an accountant, local accountant, but he hadn't been going long before the war started so he had to leave - he had to leave that you see, he was called - he was called up. Well he became a pilot - he 
b
ecome a pilot and - he flew - he - he went - he was out at Gibraltar and then he came back on a leave from Gibraltar and he was here for quite a while until he had instructions again and then they - he was - he was flying - a flying - he was flying a flyi
ng boat - to - back to Gibraltar, and they - they never arrived.
